Functions
    Declaration:
     - We can declare our functions with zero or more arguments, and also 
       returning or not a value
     - The arguments need to be variables(have $)
    
-- example

<?php 
    function sayHi($name, $age){
        echo "Hello $name, you are $age <br>";
    }

    sayHi("Harold", 25);
    sayHi("Carolina", 26);
    sayHi("Miguel", 1);

    function cube($num){
        return $num * $num * $num;
    }

    $cubeResult = cube(2);
    echo $cubeResult;
?>